data.description:
Welcome to your dream home just minutes away from Lake Anna! This stunning 3-bedroom 2 full bath property boasts modern elegance and luxurious amenities. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this brand-new home built in 2021 offers the perfect blend of comfort and sophistication.
Upon entering, you're greeted by a spacious living area adorned with exquisite wainscoting, creating a sense of warmth and charm. The adjacent dining room features the same elegant detailing, providing an ideal space for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories with loved ones.
The heart of this home lies in its beautifully appointed kitchen, complete with sleek granite countertops and equipped with convenient pull-outs. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just enjoy cooking for family and friends, you'll appreciate the functionality and style of this culinary haven.
In addition to its impeccable interior, this home showcases durable and low-maintenance luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, adding to its contemporary appeal. And let's not forget the custom blinds adorning the windows, providing both privacy and style in every room.  
Maintenance free siding on exterior and shed does convey as is.
